{
  "chapter": 345,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲、徐子陵与突利在月兰舍遭李元吉与阴癸派祝玉妍、辟守玄、边不负围攻。突利舍命强攻祝玉妍，寇徐佯攻实为回救，西突厥国师云帅突袭祝玉妍，三人趁机破墙突围。街战中阳兴会众敌我难分，迦楼罗王朱粲率骑兵入城，谢显庭驾车来救，三人脱险后与云帅会合。谢显庭为助众人脱困放火焚月兰舍，痛失同门。众人驾车逃往南门，途中遭一神秘高手伏击，此人武功诡异，掌分刚柔寒热，徐子陵拼死抵挡，寇仲助其疗伤，终驰出城门。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yu_yan",
      "speaker_name": "祝玉妍",
      "listener": "char_bi_shou_xuan",
      "text": "小心回飞之术。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 345,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_li",
      "speaker_name": "突利",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 345,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_shuai",
      "speaker_name": "云帅",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "迦楼罗兵已入城，我缠看她，三位快走！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 345,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xian_ting",
      "speaker_name": "谢显庭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上车！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 345,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_shuai",
      "speaker_name": "云帅",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "妖妇果然厉害，我必需立即运功疗伤，朱粲由北门进城，你们须在他封锁南门前，逃往城外。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 345,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_li",
      "speaker_name": "突利",
      "listener": "char_xie_xian_ting",
      "text": "到南门去！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 345,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "终有一天，我会把朱粲再逐出去。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 345,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xie_xian_ting",
      "text": "是你的小宛姑娘吧？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 345,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xian_ting",
      "speaker_name": "谢显庭",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "他们死了吗？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 345,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xie_xian_ting",
      "text": "凡人终须一死，只是先后迟早的问题。不过可堪告慰的是令师、应兄、瑕师妹和你的十多个同门及时逃生，现该安抵汉南，显庭可到汉南和他们会合。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 345,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_li",
      "speaker_name": "突利",
      "listener": "char_xie_xian_ting",
      "text": "月兰舍的火是你放的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 345,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xian_ting",
      "speaker_name": "谢显庭",
      "listener": "char_tu_li",
      "text": "我一直躲在小宛那里，见你们被李元吉的人包围，情急下只好放火，以方便你们逃走。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 345,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xian_ting",
      "speaker_name": "谢显庭",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "是否他们干的？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 345,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xie_xian_ting",
      "text": "你见到令师，自会清楚昨晚发生的事。现在甚么都不要想。你不为自己也该为小宛姑娘着想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 345,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_xie_xian_ting",
      "text": "显庭快走，迟则不及！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 345,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    }
